flowchart TD
    Start([Trigger])

    Start --> TriggerType{Jenis trigger?}
    TriggerType -->|Manual| Manual[Admin klik Anonimkan<br>di UserResource]
    TriggerType -->|Auto| Cronjob[Cronjob bulanan<br>privacy:anonymize-guest<br>privacy:anonymize-registered]

    Manual --> FindUser[Find user by ID]
    FindUser --> CheckExempt{anonymization_exempt?}
    CheckExempt -->|Ya| SkipExempt([Skip — dikecualikan])
    CheckExempt -->|Tidak| ManualSafety{Ada pesanan aktif?}

    Cronjob --> BatchQuery[Query users eligible:<br>Guest > 24 bulan<br>Registered > 36 bulan]

    BatchQuery --> GraceCheck{Dalam grace period?}
    GraceCheck -->|Ya, < 7 hari| DelayAnon([Tunda — tunggu grace period selesai])
    GraceCheck -->|Tidak| FilterExempt[Filter: anonymization_exempt = false]

    FilterExempt --> BatchSafety{Punya pesanan aktif?}
    BatchSafety -->|Ya| SkipActive([Skip — safety lock])
    BatchSafety -->|Tidak| ProcessBatch[Proses per user]

    ManualSafety -->|Ya| SkipActive
    ManualSafety -->|Tidak| ProcessAnon[AnonymizeUser action]

    ProcessBatch --> ProcessAnon

    ProcessAnon --> ActionType{User type?}
    ActionType -->|Guest| AnonGuest[Anonymize:<br>- name → Anonymous<br>- email → anon_xxx@anon<br>- phone → null<br>- recipient_name → null<br>- address_detail → null<br>- delete carts]
    ActionType -->|Registered| AnonReg[Anonymize:<br>- name → Anonymous<br>- email → anon_xxx@anon<br>- phone → null<br>- recipient_name → null<br>- address_detail → null<br>- delete carts]

    AnonGuest --> TimestampGuest[Set users.anonymized_at = now]
    AnonReg --> TimestampReg[Set users.anonymized_at = now]

    TimestampGuest --> LogAnon[Insert anonymization_logs:<br>action_type, anonymized_fields, user_id, created_at]
    TimestampReg --> LogAnon

    LogAnon --> Done([Selesai])


